DarkMouse::

She stood up and looked at Quickstrike. "Yeah, I know. It all smells 
fishy to me too. But what can we do? We can't run, we can't just 
leave them either. KitKat is a friend. She was  friend when I was 
with Megatron. She's the only one that hasn't betrayed me. And I'm 
thinking right, she's still your friend to." she said, looking up at 
Quickstrike. She knew she was right. What bothered her was the fact 
that she still had feeling for Quickstrike. She also knew that he 
didn't give a care about her, much.
